PEOPLE
v.
BELL S238339 Supreme Court of California. JUNE 13, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Review in the above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division Eight with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the case in light of People v. Contreras, et al. (2018) 4 Cal.5th 349 , 229 Cal.Rptr.3d 249 , 411 P.3d 445 . ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
